description: Reserved matters relating to Building R8 for erection of a 9-12 Storey building (excluding basement and roof levels), comprising office (class B1) and  151 residential units (class c3) (82x Social Rented Affordable and 69x market), and retail units (Flexible A1-A5 Use Class) at ground floor level as required by conditions 9, 10, 12, 14, 16-22, 24, 27, 28, 31, 33-39, 42, 42A, 43, 45, 46, 48, 49, 50A, 51, 56, 60, 61, 64-67 67 of outline planning permission reference 2004/2307/P granted 22/12/06 (subject to S106 agreement) for a comprehensive, phased, mixed-use development of former railway lands within the King's Cross Opportunity Area.
